.card.mb-3
  %h5.card-header System Status
  .card-body
    - if busy
      .aligncenter#overallgraph
      %p.text-muted.small
        The above graphs show the number of active build jobs last week,
        currently #{building_workers} of #{overall_workers} build hosts
        are busy building packages.
        At the moment #{waiting_packages} packages are waiting on the different architectures.
    %p.text-muted.small
      = host_title
      hosts
      %b= number_with_delimiter(system_stats[:projects])
      projects, with
      %b= number_with_delimiter(system_stats[:packages])
      packages, in
      %b= number_with_delimiter(system_stats[:repositories])
      repositories
      and is used by
      %b= number_with_delimiter(system_stats[:users])
      confirmed developers.
  :javascript
    plotbusyworkers(#{Webui::MonitorHelper.print_statistics_array(busy)});
